  ('dietitian-moex-00753', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-112-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '基因變異可能影響我們對食物的耐受度，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["乳糖酶（lactase,LCT）基因變異與乳製品耐受度有關", "醛脫氫酶（aldehydedehydrogenase,ALDH）基因與醇脫氫酶（alcoholdehydrogenase,ADH）基 因變異與咖啡因耐受度有關", "亞甲基四氫葉酸還原酶（methylenetetrahydrofolatereductase,MTHFR）基因變異與葉酸需要量有關", "人類白血球抗原（humanleukocyteantigen,HLA）基因變異與麩質耐受度有關"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8a509cae941f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "36a63784849d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112030", "c": "101", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 36, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00754', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-112-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於類固醇（steroids）荷爾蒙與蛋白質／多胜肽（proteins/polypeptides）荷爾蒙的比較，下列何者 正確？', '["類固醇（steroids）荷爾蒙於血液中不需要運輸蛋白（transportproteins）", "類固醇（steroids）荷爾蒙於血漿中之半衰期較短（數分鐘）", "蛋白質／多胜肽（proteins/polypeptides）荷爾蒙之受器（receptors）多位於細胞內", "蛋白質／多胜肽（proteins/polypeptides）荷爾蒙作用調節者（mediator）可為鈣離子（Ca2+）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8a509cae941f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "36a63784849d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112030", "c": "101", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 37, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00755', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-112-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於真核生物（eukaryotes）mRNA 轉錄作用（transcription）的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["RNA聚合酶II（RNApolymeraseII）可與增強子（enhancer）及啟動子（promoter）結合，調節 轉錄作用", "過程中會保留內含子（intron），因其為主要譯碼（coding）區域", "過程中包括RNA剪接（splicing），主要將所有內含子（intron）拼接在一起", "最後形成之mRNA在3’末端會加上帽子結構（capping）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8a509cae941f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "36a63784849d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112030", "c": "101", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 38, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
